> <span begin="01:02.769" end="01:03.091">a</span><span begin="01:03.091" end="01:04.681">round</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没有了希望只剩苟延残喘</span></p><p begin="01:06.644" end="01:12.094" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="01:06.644" end="01:07.520">Crushed</span> <span begin="01:07.520" end="01:08.141">like</span> <span begin="01:08.141" end="01:09.032">a</span> <span begin="01:09.032" end="01:09.719">bug</span> <span begin="01:09.719" end="01:09.919">in</span> <span begin="01:09.919" end="01:10.257">the</span> <span begin="01:10.257" end="01:12.094">ground</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">像一只被压扁在地上的爬虫</span></p><p begin="01:13.648" end="01:18.427" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="01:13.648" end="01:14.545">Let</span> <span begin="01:14.545" end="01:15.236">down</span> <span begin="01:15.236" end="01:16.194">and</span> <span begin="01:16.194" end="01:16.708">hang</span><span begin="01:16.708" end="01:16.985">ing</span> <span begin="01:16.985" end="01:17.221">a</span><span begin="01:17.221" end="01:18.427">round</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">绝望但还在苟延残喘着</span></p><p begin="01:30.358" end="01:34.671" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="01:30.358" end="01:31.391">Shell</span> <span begin="01:31.391" end="01:32.326">smashed,</span> <span begin="01:32.725" end="01:32.956">jui</span><span begin="01:32.956" end="01:33.485">ces</span> <span begin="01:33.485" end="01:34.320">flo</span><span begin="01:34.320" end="01:34.671">wing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">支离破碎 汁液横流</span></p><p begin="01:34.671" end="01:39.391" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:34.671" end="01:36.087">Wings</span> <span begin="01:36.087" end="01:36.950">twitch,</span> <span begin="01:37.380" end="01:37.592">legs</span> <span begin="01:37.592" end="01:38.188">are</span> <span begin="01:38.188" end="01:38.795">go</span><span begin="01:38.795" end="01:39.391">ing</span><span ttm